cs.AI, cs.DB, cs.LO, cs.LG, cs.CL. 

This paper deals with answering queries over knowledge bases, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and databases (cs.DB). The use of the tableau algorithm and description logics also suggests a connection to logic (cs.LO) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the use of blocking conditions for reasoning with rules suggests a connection to natural language processing (cs.CL).
